CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Northrim BanCorp Inc is a bank holding company. The company operates in two segments: Community Banking and Home Mortgage Lending. It generates maximum revenue from the Community Banking segment. It offers to spend and save products such as checking, savings, money market accounts, debit cards, cashback rewards, and credit cards. It also includes loans and credit lines, mortgage loans, investment, and plan products.
